/obj/item/reagent_containers/hypospray/stealthinjector/itchingpowder/attack(mob/living/M, mob/user)
	. = ..()
	update_icon()

/obj/item/reagent_containers/hypospray/stealthinjector/itchingpowder/update_icon()
